data.description: Discover the incredible potential to transform this property into the home of your dreams! Situated in the idyllic setting of the charming and established Brightmoor neighborhood, the home is perfectly positioned on a private lot, surrounded by mature trees, landscaped lot & is accessible by 2 separate cul-de-sacs. Positioned close to the back of the neighborhood, traffic is minimal. The generously sized bedrooms each boast walk-in closets. Step inside to find a well-designed layout featuring a convenient home office with elegant French doors, a cozy living room with a classic brick fireplace, a separate dining room, & a kitchen with an adjacent breakfast nook. This thoughtfully priced home considers necessary improvements & outstanding features, inviting you to envision its extraordinary potential. Seize the opportunity to renovate & add your personalized touch, unlocking the door to the delightful possibilities of crafting this residence into a truly unique and exceptional home!
